{"tid":1385593,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"呢2個幾月香港人令我好感動 香港人真係好痴線","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:11:56.000Z","uid":151061,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e4fbac131ae3402fe27d7c42a5ac2058bced00a3","tid":1385593,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:15:43.000Z","msg":"對唔住 我係一個好遲先發夢既人<br />\n6月開始 參加不同遊行、集會<br />\n就算企後排、行到成身汗、病左都要出席<br />\n我唔敢話我個個集會、遊行都有幫到手<br />\n每次完左 返到屋企訓唔著 都要睇住d集會片喊<br />\n好心痛、好無力、好憤怒、好心酸<br />\n家中有2老藍絲 希望有日會改變佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我好自豪身邊都有你地 個個香港人都好好<br />\n食完催淚彈會哮喘 為左唔做你地負擔<br />\n我都會留係後排 要幫手就幫手 默默文宣支持你地<br />\n之後我希望可以繼續見到每個手足<br />\n陪我見證時代革命、我地香港人既成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下d痴線post係d好癲既人開 傳開去<br />\n令佢地做既野更有意義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果義士冇錢食飯 歡迎嚟錫克廟 有免費三餐食<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382123</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［急推］HKTVmall員工助養小朋友計劃正式啟動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我警告你班細蚊仔唔好再覺得自己佔咗人便宜啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382375</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為一個學生，我想同大家道個歉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383753</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b5408364df775ec3da51b40b7f82f75d2b71c4d5","tid":1385593,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:45:32.000Z","msg":"8.5罷工"},{"pid":"50dd1e0fcdbf3085530e570ad339a6aa7baed8a3","tid":1385593,"uid":100016,"like":1,"disli